ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: A good overview of demography--what it is, what types of transitions have occurred throughout history and why, what the policy implications for these changes might be, etc.I would absolutely recommend this course to anyone interested in demography, anthropology, and/or development
I would highly recommend the course to anybody interested in demography.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This class worked very nicely with my other course on development economics and in general it helped me to understand key development issues in new and more nuanced ways. I am actually using the final paper of this class (combined with another paper) for my final thesis for the program, so it was clearly directly relevant.
help me have more knowledge of all the topics. good beginning level/introduction course.
